      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary specimen, maintained in absolute mint condition. This vehicle represents a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing short of perfection. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, reflects a standard of care that is truly peerless. Mechanically superior and aesthetically indistinguishable from new, this motorcar stands as a testament to automotive excellence and meticulous ownership.",
      "price": 48900.0,
