    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a true time-capsule vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory-original luster, completely free of stone chips, swirl marks, or blemishes. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine state; the premium leather seats show zero bolster wear, the dashboard is flawless, and it still carries that distinct new-car aroma. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a comprehensive service history with every scheduled maintenance performed by master technicians. Every button, switch, and electronic feature operates with factory precision. Garage-kept under a climate-controlled cover and never driven in inclement weather, this vehicle represents the absolute pinnacle of preservation for this model.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
